<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>When constructed, this will configure the given serial port, including marking the relevant pins as alternate function.</para>

<para>NOTE: Unlike the Mbed RawSerial class, this will use 8X oversampling when necessary to achieve higher baud rates. </para>
